ts in June not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"3a41dd3ac2f038f51d320b935ac6633ede02f9dc","tid":1406484,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:12:49.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子 黑社會 強姦犯 狗<br />\n佢地唔配叫警"},{"pid":"7e0e4dfccf55ee4bd9371c5aa403cb630ca8596c","tid":1406484,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f718a4def9640365642af7b0870db759ef1993d8","tid":1406484,"uid":279695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:07:54.000Z","msg":"香港警察 慣性強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港警察 休班雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港警察 愛滋病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港警察 性病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子 黑社會 強姦犯 狗<br />\n佢地唔配叫警"},{"pid":"d336b6a27f7f9e21816957d56827dd368092860a","tid":1406484,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:13:35.000Z","msg":"屌，唔小心負評咗，sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18381c64a36160cc86a7e19fdeb8694be4017ce","tid":1406484,"uid":129537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f72aa5789e64bc988005fa261a32f26f579e586","tid":1406484,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"1. 黑社會<br />\n2. 不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意<br />\n3. 殺人兇手<br />\n<br />\n仲有句<br />\n4. 知法犯法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:14:55.000Z","msg":"依加可以加多句<br />\n強姦犯"},{"pid"